---
/**
 * CROManifesto — "Why Men Choose Us"
 * Navy section with split layout: copy + testimonial on left, team image on right.
 */
---

<section
  style="background: var(--cro-surface-secondary); padding: var(--section-y) 24px; overflow: hidden;"
>
  <div class="manifesto-grid">
    <!-- Copy — left on desktop, second on mobile -->
    <div class="manifesto-copy">
      <!-- Eyebrow -->
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.8125rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--orange); margin-bottom: 12px;">
        WHY MEN CHOOSE US
      </p>

      <!-- Heading -->
      <h2
        style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h1); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 1.05; color: var(--cro-text-on-light); margin-bottom: 24px;"
      >
        Your labs might be normal.<br />
        You still don&rsquo;t feel right.
      </h2>

      <!-- Body paragraphs -->
      <p
        style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-body); color: var(--cro-text-body); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; max-width: 580px;"
      >
        Most men wait two years before saying something out loud. They get
        bloodwork. Their GP says everything looks fine. They go home. Nothing
        changes.
      </p>
      <p
        style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-body); color: var(--cro-text-body); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 32px; max-width: 580px;"
      >
        We specialize in men&rsquo;s health. One licensed provider, your labs, and
        a real conversation. Not a coordinator reading from a tablet. A real,
        in-person conversation about how you actually feel. If treatment is
        right for you, you leave with a plan the same day.
      </p>

      <!-- Testimonial card — white with shadow -->
      <div
        style="background: var(--cro-surface-primary); border: 1px solid rgba(11,16,41,0.10); border-radius: var(--cro-card-radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow-card); padding: 32px; margin-bottom: 28px;"
      >
        <!-- Quote icon -->
        <svg
          width="20"
          height="20"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="var(--orange)"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          aria-hidden="true"
          style="margin-bottom: 12px; opacity: 0.7;"
        >
          <path d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z" />
          <path d="M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z" />
        </svg>
        <p
          style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-body); color: var(--cro-text-body); font-style: italic; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;"
        >
          &ldquo;Saw two GPs who told me my levels were fine. I knew they weren&rsquo;t.
          Three weeks after starting treatment I was sleeping through the
          night again. The difference in energy over the next few months was
          something no standard lab panel ever captured.&rdquo;
        </p>
        <p
          style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--cro-text-on-light); margin-bottom: 4px;"
        >
          James T., 48, Norfolk
        </p>
        <p
          style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted-gray);"
        >
          Verified member. Individual results vary.
        </p>
      </div>

      <a
        href="#hero-form"
        style="display: inline-block; background: var(--orange); color: var(--white); font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none; padding: 16px 32px; border-radius: var(--radius-btn, 6px);"
      >
        BOOK YOUR 60-MINUTE VISIT
      </a>
      <p
        style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted-gray); margin-top: 12px;"
      >
        No-obligation in-person visit. Individual results vary.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Image — right on desktop, first on mobile -->
    <div class="manifesto-image">
      <img
        src="/images/photos/member-richmond.jpg"
        alt="Men's Wellness Centers member, Richmond Virginia"
        loading="lazy"
        width={800}
        height={600}
        style="width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 12px; object-fit: cover; box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
